{
  "stem": "1530.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was one of the officers on the ship.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we arrived, two weeks later, he married my sister, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Chicha. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, the point is though, that when we arrived in this country, on May 8th, 1945, I think the war was over May 8th or May 10th.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us to like, an hearing room again with the FBI.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had Hungarian interpreters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to tell our whole story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't have any papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because they--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have the address.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow, they let us into this country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- because we were, I think, the first ones from Auschwitz to come and tell them the truth, what happened there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because they really saw that my father is living in this country, they let us into my father's-- what is it?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Cognisance or something, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was like the guardian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Guardian, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just another day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they first took us to Baltimore with the ship.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there the Jewish Women's Council took care of us at a beautiful house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father came up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he saw in men's uniforms, he got purple in his face.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he didn't want his beautiful, young daughters to be like men, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And trouble started immediately with my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, he accused us and me, you killed your mother because you got away from religion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I said to my father, you know, there is no God in this world.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because God would not ever looked down on Auschwitz and let that happen to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And how does a little rotter has the nerve to say this to her father?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was so angry.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
